  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168450/extras/15ba9074a7f2987a363de0c459eaeb35.poster.avif?t=1674006450\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168450/extras/15ba9074a7f2987a363de0c459eaeb35.webm?t=1674006450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Enter into the DreamWilds, a multilayered continuum created by the unconscious thoughts of living beings!<br><br>As a knight ripped from his dying world, you must explore the depths of the DreamWilds, and discover the source of the violence that is rotting these worlds.<br>Along the way, you'll encounter strange enemies and bizarre entities, all driven mad by a dark ancient power.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Crazy Fast Paced Gameplay!</h2>DREAMWILD is a fast paced first person arcade style game. Shoot for a high score as you attempt to survive multiple infinite worlds, each with their own unique bizarre enemies and strange sights to see! Speed around at mach speed, and use any tool you can find to your advantage!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Eccentric Velocity Movement System!</h2>DREAMWILD features a unique and fluid movement system! Strafe, surf, and gain speed to outrun and outwit your enemies!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Unique Arsenal of Tools!</h2>All sorts of strange tools and weapons can be found in the DreamWilds, each guaranteed to radically change your play style! You might become a Vacuuming Knight, or a Cursed Knight, or even a Fishing Knight!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bizarre 2D Rendered Worlds?</h2>When in a safe zone, DREAMWILD shifts view, and now you'll find yourself in high detailed prerendered worlds! Explore the Dream Castle, Interact with otherworldly characters, and make friends from the DreamWilds!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168450/extras/76db2fadce91bb15536064ce6f6fdcba.poster.avif?t=1674006450\" width=112 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168450/extras/76db2fadce91bb15536064ce6f6fdcba.webm?t=1674006450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168450/extras/76db2fadce91bb15536064ce6f6fdcba.poster.avif?t=1674006450\" width=112 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168450/extras/76db2fadce91bb15536064ce6f6fdcba.webm?t=1674006450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168450/extras/76db2fadce91bb15536064ce6f6fdcba.poster.avif?t=1674006450\" width=112 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168450/extras/76db2fadce91bb15536064ce6f6fdcba.webm?t=1674006450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168450/extras/76db2fadce91bb15536064ce6f6fdcba.poster.avif?t=1674006450\" width=112 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168450/extras/76db2fadce91bb15536064ce6f6fdcba.webm?t=1674006450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168450/extras/76db2fadce91bb15536064ce6f6fdcba.poster.avif?t=1674006450\" width=112 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168450/extras/76db2fadce91bb15536064ce6f6fdcba.webm?t=1674006450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
